             was indicted for <rs id="t18261207-215-off1260" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18261207-215-off1260" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18261207-215-off1260" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18261207-215-cd1261" type="crimeDate">1st of November</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261207-215-off1260 t18261207-215-cd1261"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 4s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18261207-215-victim1215" type="victimName">
                        George Joseph 
                        Wilson
                     <interp inst="t18261207-215-victim1215" type="surname" value="Wilson"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18261207-215-victim1215" type="given" value="George Joseph"></interp>
